- ✅ `[GeneratedRegex]` used for 3 patterns on .NET 7+ — good dual-targeting via `#if`
- ✅ `RegexOptions.Compiled` used for downlevel (`#else`) static fields — correct fallback
- ✅ `IsAllUpperCase` uses `foreach` over `string` instead of LINQ `.All()` — zero allocation
- ✅ `IsAsciiAlphanumeric` and `WordCount` use manual `foreach` — efficient
- ✅ `Slugify` uses `.ToLowerInvariant()` — correct culture handling

